🧭 ELEVATOR PITCH (FOR “THE MESSAGE VAULT”)
The Message Vault is an emotional delivery service that lets you send someone you care about daily encouragement—anonymously at first. It’s the simplest way to support someone from a distance, spark healing, or say what you can’t always say out loud.

Alternate punchier options:

“Send powerful messages. Stay anonymous. Heal together.”

“Say everything… without saying it yet.”

“Support someone without the pressure of being present.”

